description: Teacher for Alexa is a fun and interactive way to learn basic math through a series of simple addition, subtraction, and multiplication problems. Example level:  What is 7 times 2?
exampleInteractions: Alexa, ask Teacher to teach me addition.
Alexa, tell Teacher to help me with multiplication.
name: Teacher for Alexa
shortDescription: Teacher for Alexa is a fun and interactive way to learn basic math through a series of simple addition, subtraction, and multiplication problems.
